/***************************************************************
* Simple network firewall. 
* Accept all TCP apckets with destiantion port value equals to 
* filt_destination_port, and drop others. 
* All packets, that accepted will be modifyed by
* filter:
*   1) Changed destination IP to mod_destination_ip
*   2) Changed source port to mod_source_port
*   3) Changed first byte in data of packet to mod_first_byte
***************************************************************/


